{"title":"學習基礎 Presudo Code","uid":"a36a827eaa09142da6be8a3fdbdea209","slug":"學習基礎-Presudo-Code","date":"2021-04-28T19:17:48.000Z","updated":"2022-08-01T20:40:23.381Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/學習基礎-Presudo-Code.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>虛擬碼的風格差異很大，有些會用數學表示法 (mathematical notation)，有些會用口語敘述，有些會接近真正的程式碼。沒有那一種風格是最好的，要看當下的需求來決定。</p>\n<p>學習虛擬碼就像學習程式語言，只要針對不同情境撰寫相對應的虛擬碼，再將其組合起來即可。一般來說，程式設計常見的情境如下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>宣告 (declaration)</li>\n<li>指派 (assignment)</li>\n<li>代數運算 (algebraic operations)</li>\n<li>選擇 (selection)</li>\n<li>迭代 (iteration)</li>\n<li>函式 (function)</li>\n<li>類別 (class)</li>\n<li>陣列 (array)</li>\n<li>集合 (collections)<br>我們只要針對這些情境撰寫相對應的虛擬碼，大概就可以抓到虛擬碼的寫法。學習其他人的虛擬碼也是用相同的要訣去拆解各種不同的情境即可。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"學習重點\"><a href=\"#學習重點\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"學習重點\"></a>學習重點</h2><p>這次是挑選常用語法來實作</p>\n<h3 id=\"LowerCase\"><a href=\"#LowerCase\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LowerCase()\"></a>LowerCase()</h3><p>toLowerCase() 方法用來將字串中的英文字母都轉成小寫。</p>\n<p>語法：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">str.toLowerCase()</code></pre>\n\n<p>用法：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">console.log(&#39;Hello World&#39;.toLowerCase());\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 輸出 &#39;hello world&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"UpperCase\"><a href=\"#UpperCase\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"UpperCase()\"></a>UpperCase()</h3><p>toUpperCase() 方法用來將字串中的英文字母都轉成大寫。</p>\n<p>語法：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">str.toUpperCase()</code></pre>\n\n<p>用法：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">console.log(&#39;Hello World&#39;.toUpperCase());\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 輸出 &#39;HELLO WORLD&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"GetLastWord\"><a href=\"#GetLastWord\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GetLastWord()\"></a>GetLastWord()</h3><p>取得輸入字串的最後一個字元</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">function GetLastWord(inputValue) &#123;\n  return inputValue.charAt(str.length - 1);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"實作練習\"><a href=\"#實作練習\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實作練習\"></a>實作練習</h2><p><a href=\"https://michael0520.github.io/Presudo_Code_Practice/index.html\">Page</a></p>\n","text":"虛擬碼的風格差異很大，有些會用數學表示法 (mathematical notation)，有些會用口語敘述，有些會接近真正的程式碼。沒有那一種風格是最好的，要看當下的需求來決定。 學習虛擬碼就像學習程式語言，只要針對不同情境撰寫相對應的虛擬碼，再將其組合起來即可。一般來說，程式設...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":827,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":46,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":42,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">學習重點</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#LowerCase\"><span class=\"toc-text\">LowerCase()</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#UpperCase\"><span class=\"toc-text\">UpperCase()</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#GetLastWord\"><span class=\"toc-text\">GetLastWord()</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E7%B7%B4%E7%BF%92\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實作練習</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title